{0 Spotify_ml}

This library provides OCaml bindings for accessing the Spotify Web API.

{1 Usage}

The {!Spotify_ml.Api} module provides all functions and types that match the Spotify Web API.
To use it, you need to first create a {!Spotify_ml.Client} and optionally a {!Spotify_ml.Client.User}
if you want to access user specific information such as a user's top tracks.
